description: Erection of a building comprising basement plus 23 storey building (with roof terrace) providing (i) parking, plant and 755mý of Class A1, A2 or A3 (retail, office and food and drink) uses at basement level; (ii) 1,367mý of either Class A1, A2, A3, D2 (retail, food and drink, and leisure) uses on the ground floor; (iii) 1,609mý of either Class A1, A2, A3, B1, D1 (retail, food and drink, offices or leisure (D2) uses on the first floor; (iv) 8,430mý of offices (Class B1) on the 2nd to 6th floors; and (v) 217 residential units on the 7th to 22nd floors, together alterations to the entrance of the Aldgate Station Underground Station - Amendment to scheme approved in September 2002 (Ref: PA/02/0074).
